-- Founder Technology Plans to Raise as Much as $168 Million in Rights Offer
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-28T23:41:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/founder-technology-plans-to-raise-as-much-as-168-million-in-rights-offer.html

          
          
             Founder Technology Group Corp. aims
to raise as much as 1.14 billion yuan ($167 million) in a rights
offer.  
 The Chinese computer products maker will offer a total of
517.9 million shares, or 3 shares for every 10 shares held by
shareholders, for 2.2 yuan apiece.   
 Founder Technology made the announcement in a statement to
the Shanghai Stock Exchange.  
